}, {\"sentence\": \"But there were two big problems with the IBA's decision to disqualify Khelif and Lin - both of whom have been competing in the sport for yearsand whose passports confirm that they are women.\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4187, \"end\": 4190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999859548965547, \"rank\": 1.4045300437911359e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two big problems\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4222}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 4227, \"to\": 4230}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4278}, {\"ngram\": \"yearsand\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4291}, {\"ngram\": \"whose passports\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4307}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First, the boxing association was not acting in accordancewith its official regulations.\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boxing association\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4367}, {\"ngram\": \"its official regulations\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOChas since statedthat the IBA \\\"suddenly\\\" disqualified the women from the 2023 World Championships \\\"without any due process\\\" and that the decision was \\\"contrary to good governance.\\\"\", \"from\": 4427, \"to\": 4613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4459, \"end\": 4462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999859548965547, \"rank\": 1.4045300437911359e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\