ernational_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.882276776196792e-46, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4791, \"end\": 4794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999859548965547, \"rank\": 1.4045300437911359e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 4868, \"end\": 4874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8399253519602406e-20, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4708}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4720}, {\"ngram\": \"governance\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"ethics\", \"from\": 4762, \"to\": 4768}, {\"ngram\": \"its official recognition\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4862}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic tournament\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Boxing Unit relied on the IBA's established eligibility requirements, drafted after the 2016 Rio Games, which had allowed Khelif and Lin to compete.\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 5080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4921, \"end\": 4931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9811893148148446e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4932, \"end\": 4938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8399253519602406e-20, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 4958, \"end\": 4961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999859548965547, \"rank\": 1.4045300437911359e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Rio Games\", \"from\": 5016, \"to\": 5034}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those same requirements also allowed the two women to compete in the 2020 Olympic Games, where Khelif finished in fifth place and Lin finished ninth.\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those same requirements\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5104}, {\"ngram\": \"the two women\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5131}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5168}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5182}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth place\", \"from\": 5195, \"to\": 5206}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's second-round Olympic victory over Carini sparked predictable if dispiriting outcry fromultra-conservative politiciansandanti-transgender influencers.\", \"from\": 5232, \"to\": 5390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5275, \"end\": 5281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9997079843319976, \"rank\": 0.00029210096595091, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's second-round Olympic victory\", \"from\": 5232, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"outcry fromultra-conservative politiciansandanti-transgender influencers\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif must be a \\\"a male.\\\"\", \"from\": 5392, \"to\": 5418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5392, \"to\": 5398}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"a male\", \"from\": 5407, \"to\": 5416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(She's not.)\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or she's \\\"transgender.\\\"\", \"from\": 5432, \"to\": 5455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Again, she's not.\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, it's illegal in Algeria to identify as such.)\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5500, \"end\": 5507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999999994769496, \"rank\": 5.230292301830707e-09, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others have claimed Khelif's \\\"biological advantages\\\" are \\\"unfair.\\\"\", \"from\": 5531, \"to\": 5597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 5531, \"to\": 5537}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's \\\"biological advantages\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But are not the Olympic Games meant to showcase biological advantages?\", \"from\": 5599, \"to\": 5669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5628}, {\"ngram\": \"biological advantages\", \"from\": 5647, \"to\": 5668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it's Simone Biles' abilityto leap 12 feet off the groundduring her floor routine, or swimmerKatie Ledeckyowning all 20 of the fastest women's 1,500-meter freestyle times in history, no one gets to the top without superlative athletic gifts.\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles' abilityto leap\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5711}, {\"ngram\": \"the groundduring her floor routine\", \"from\": 5724, \"to\": 5758}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest women's 1,500-meter freestyle times\", \"from\": 5800, \"to\": 5847}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 5860, \"to\": 5866}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"superlative athletic gifts\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Left out of the discussion was the fact that Khelif did what boxers are supposed to do: hit their opponents hard enough that they can not hit back.\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 6067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the discussion\", \"from\": 5932, \"to\": 5946}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 5951, \"to\": 5959}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5965, \"to\": 5971}, {\"ngram\": \"boxers\", \"from\": 5981, \"to\": 5987}, {\"ngram\": \"their opponents\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin's fights, which ended with decisions in her favor, were less controversial.\", \"from\": 6068, \"to\": 6148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin's fights\", \"from\": 6068, \"to\": 6080}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 6099, \"to\": 6108}, {\"ngram\": \"her favor\", \"from\": 6112, \"to\": 6121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they have nevertheless spurred further debate about who should be allowed to compete in women's sports.\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"further debate\", \"from\": 6184, \"to\": 6198}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 6241, \"to\": 6255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Games are the closest the Olympics have come to gender parity:49% of all Olympic athletes this year are women.\", \"from\": 6258, \"to\": 6378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Games\", \"from\": 6258, \"to\": 6273}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6302}, {\"ngram\": \"gender\", \"from\": 6316, \"to\": 6322}, {\"ngram\": \"parity:49%\", \"from\": 6323, \"to\": 6333}, {\"ngram\": \"all Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 6337, \"to\": 6357}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6372, \"to\": 6377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing has been among the slowest sports to add opportunities for women.\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6386}, {\"ngram\": \"the slowest sports\", \"from\": 6402, \"to\": 6420}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 6428, \"to\": 6441}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6446, \"to\": 6451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women first competed in Olympic boxing at the 2012 London Games, under just three weight classes.\", \"from\": 6453, \"to\": 6550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 6453, \"to\": 6458}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic boxing\", \"from\": 6477, \"to\": 6491}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 London Games\", \"from\": 6495, \"to\": 6516}, {\"ngram\": \"just three weight classes\", \"from\": 6524, \"to\": 6549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In comparison, men fought in 10 different weight categories.\", \"from\": 6551, \"to\": 6611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 6554, \"to\": 6564}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 6566, \"to\": 6569}, {\"ngram\": \"10 different weight categories\", \"from\": 6580, \"to\": 6610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2016 Rio Games saw the same disparity.\", \"from\": 6612, \"to\": 6654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2016 Rio Games\", \"from\": 6612, \"to\": 6630}, {\"ngram\": \"the same disparity\", \"from\": 6635, \"to\": 6653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the 2020 Games, there were five categories for women and eight for men.\", \"from\": 6655, \"to\": 6729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Games\", \"from\": 6658, \"to\": 6672}, {\"ngram\": \"five categories\", \"from\": 6685, \"to\": 6700}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6705, \"to\": 6710}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 6725, \"to\": 6728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's Games include six weight classes for women and seven for men.\", \"from\": 6730, \"to\": 6803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This year's Games\", \"from\": 6730, \"to\": 6747}, {\"ngram\": \"six weight classes\", \"from\": 6756, \"to\": 6774}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6779, \"to\": 6784}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 6799, \"to\": 6802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport's binary organization is not perfect, but it is important.\", \"from\": 6805, \"to\": 6869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport's binary organization\", \"from\": 6805, \"to\": 6832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Research finds that, on average, elite male athletes outperform elite female athletesby about 10% to 12%.The wonderful strides made in women's sportswould likely be undone by eliminating gender categories.\", \"from\": 6871, \"to\": 7076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Research\", \"from\": 6871, \"to\": 6879}, {\"ngram\": \"elite male athletes\", \"from\": 6904, \"to\": 6923}, {\"ngram\": \"elite female athletesby\", \"from\": 6935, \"to\": 6958}, {\"ngram\": \"12%.The wonderful strides\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 6997}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sportswould\", \"from\": 7006, \"to\": 7025}, {\"ngram\": \"gender categories\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, the ways sports governing bodies define and police those categories not only disadvantage gender-diverse athletes, but also cast aspersions on any female athlete who may strike someone as \\\"masculine\\\" - in performance, appearance or otherwise.\", \"from\": 7077, \"to\": 7337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 7080, \"to\": 7093}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 7095, \"to\": 7103}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 7104, \"to\": 7110}, {\"ngram\": \"bodies\", \"from\": 7121, \"to\": 7127}, {\"ngram\": \"those categories\", \"from\": 7146, \"to\": 7162}, {\"ngram\": \"not only disadvantage gender-diverse athletes\", \"from\": 7163, \"to\": 7208}, {\"ngram\": \"aspersions\", \"from\": 7224, \"to\": 7234}, {\"ngram\": \"any female athlete\", \"from\": 7238, \"to\": 7256}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 7272, \"to\": 7279}, {\"ngram\": \"masculine\", \"from\": 7284, \"to\": 7293}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 7300, \"to\": 7311}, {\"ngram\": \"appearance\", \"from\": 7313, \"to\": 7323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To return to the issue of protection: Who or what do sex-based regulations protect?\", \"from\": 7339, \"to\": 7422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 7352, \"to\": 7361}, {\"ngram\": \"protection\", \"from\": 7365, \"to\": 7375}, {\"ngram\": \"sex-based regulations\", \"from\": 7392, \"to\": 7413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do they protect a never-level, level playing field?\", \"from\": 7423, \"to\": 7474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a never-level, level playing field\", \"from\": 7439, \"to\": 7473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The indefinable category of \\\"woman?\\\"\", \"from\": 7475, \"to\": 7511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The indefinable category\", \"from\": 7475, \"to\": 7499}, {\"ngram\": \"woman\", \"from\": 7504, \"to\": 7509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or women's safety in an unsafe sport?\", \"from\": 7512, \"to\": 7549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Or women's safety\", \"from\": 7512, \"to\": 7529}, {\"ngram\": \"an unsafe sport\", \"from\": 7533, \"to\": 7548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport itself?\", \"from\": 7550, \"to\": 7563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 7550, \"to\": 7555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not really know what criteria the IBA used to disqualify Khelif and Lin, although there is plenty of speculation.\", \"from\": 7565, \"to\": 7684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7605, \"end\": 7608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999859548965547, \"rank\": 1.4045300437911359e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7634}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 7639, \"to\": 7642}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 7662, \"to\": 7668}, {\"ngram\": \"speculation\", \"from\": 7672, \"to\": 7683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But these are personal, intimate details that, in my view, should be respected and remain private.\", \"from\": 7685, \"to\": 7783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"personal, intimate details\", \"from\": 7699, \"to\": 7725}, {\"ngram\": \"my view\", \"from\": 7735, \"to\": 7742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What we do know is that the furor has far-reaching consequences.Khelif has begged for the hateful discourse to stop: \\\"It can destroy people, it can kill people's thoughts, spirit and mind.\", \"from\": 7785, \"to\": 7973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the furor\", \"from\": 7809, \"to\": 7818}, {\"ngram\": \"far-reaching consequences\", \"from\": 7823, \"to\": 7848}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 7849, \"to\": 7855}, {\"ngram\": \"the hateful discourse\", \"from\": 7871, \"to\": 7892}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7918, \"to\": 7924}, {\"ngram\": \"people's thoughts\", \"from\": 7938, \"to\": 7955}, {\"ngram\": \"spirit\", \"from\": 7957, \"to\": 7963}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 7968, \"to\": 7972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can divide people.\\\"\", \"from\": 7974, \"to\": 7996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7988, \"to\": 7994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It already has.\", \"from\": 7998, \"to\": 8013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a Games that has so brilliantly showcased and celebrated female Olympians, I see the debate over Khelif and Lin as distracting as it is heartbreaking.\", \"from\": 8015, \"to\": 8168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 8018, \"to\": 8025}, {\"ngram\": \"female Olympians\", \"from\": 8075, \"to\": 8091}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"from\": 8099, \"to\": 8109}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 8115, \"to\": 8121}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 8126, \"to\": 8129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Above all, both boxers are human beings who do not deserve to be made into political punching bags.\", \"from\": 8169, \"to\": 8268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both boxers\", \"from\": 8180, \"to\": 8191}, {\"ngram\": \"human beings\", \"from\": 8196, \"to\": 8208}, {\"ngram\": \"political punching bags\", \"from\": 8244, \"to\": 8267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 8270, \"to\": 8324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 8270, \"to\": 8324}]}]}"